cleaned_text: [ The Mood Factor ](https://naturalmedicinenh.com/event/the-mood-factor/) Anxiety and depression are a common experience for many of us and the people we love. Join us to explore the many factors involved in these mood imbalances. Find out how naturopathic medicine can help! At this talk, we will discuss how to get on the right path to correct these imbalances naturally.
